>>>> installed packages and needed PHP dependencies: 
•	 Install Apache2 web server and PHP 7.4.
#sudo apt-get install apache2 php7.4 -y 
•	Install MySQL server, client, and development libraries.
#sudo apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client libmysqlclient-dev -y 
•	Install additional PHP plugins required by Moodle.
#sudo apt-get install php7.4-gd php7.4-intl php7.4-xmlrpc php7.4-soap php7.4-zip php7.4-mbstring -y.
